Our group is a diverse mix of developers, squad leads, DevOps engineers, designers, and marketers. We are looking for a Senior Software Developer to join the WorkingMouse team and play a key role in shaping high-quality solutions while supporting and mentoring others.

What's in it for you? 

Platform engineering: youÆll have exposure to working with modern tech frameworks and our in-house Codebots technology. 
